val vCookBook = [

("Burger", ["Patty", "Bread", "Bread", "Sauce", "Vegetable"], (5.0,7.0)),
("Double Burger", ["Patty", "Patty", "Bread", "Bread", "Sauce", "Vegetable"], (7.0,9.0)),
("Cheese Burger", ["Patty", "Patty", "Bread", "Cheese", "Sauce", "Vegetable"], (7.0,9.0)),

("Fries", ["Potatoes", "Sauce"], (1.0,2.0)),

("Burger Menu", ["Burger", "Fries", "Drink"], (2.0,3.0)),
("Double Burger Menu", ["Double Burger", "Fries", "Drink"], (2.0,3.0)),
("Cheese Burger Menu", ["Cheese Burger", "Fries", "Drink"], (2.0,3.0))

];

val vMenu = [
"Burger", "Burger",
"Double Burger",  "Double Burger",  
"Cheese Burger", 
"Fries", "Fries", "Fries", "Fries", 
"Drink",
"Burger Menu", "Burger Menu", 
"Double Burger Menu", "Double Burger Menu", 
"Cheese Burger Menu"];

fun chooseItem () =
(* picks a random item from the menu *)
let 
  val c = discrete(1,length vMenu)
in
  List.nth(vMenu, c-1) 
end;

let
  fun predBindElem (Customer'consume (1, {its,oid,s})) = 
            (not (mem its "Burger" orelse 
                    mem its "Double Burger" orelse
                    mem its "Cheese Burger" orelse 
                    mem its "Burger Menu" orelse
                    mem its "Cheese Burger Menu" orelse
                    mem its "Double Burger Menu" orelse
                    mem its "Fries"))
      | predBindElem _ = false
in
  predBindElem bindelem  
end
